- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of a Gaussian Prior to reduce overfitting in the models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the computational complexity of training models. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of an informative sample to reduce computational complexity. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category as the paper does not seem to be related to sound or audio processing.
